MediaMix Multimedia Player


 

 

MediaMix Multimedia Player

Version - 1.0

 

MediaMix Multimedia Player is an advanced media player that provides various features and rich experience, supporting most of the audio and video formats.


Features


- All in one bundled package as it offers both audio and video playbacks

- Supports and plays 4k videos of over 100GB flawlessly

- Modern and responsive UI

- User friendly alerts

- Has support for SRT and VTT subtitle file formats

System Requirements


CPU - Intel Core 2 Duo or higher

RAM - 1 GB or higher

HDD - 200MB of disk space required

Mouse and keyboard are required

Directx9.0c or higher is required

.Net Framework 4.5.2 or higher
 

Microsoft Visual C++ 2005 - 2019 is required

FAQ


1. How to revert back or enable windowed mode after MediaMix Multimedia Player goes in fullscreen mode?

Answer

If MediaMix Multimedia Player is in fullscreen mode, then simply press 'Esc' i.e 'Escape' key of keyboard to revert back to or enable windowed mode.


2.Why don't some .SRT files get loaded into MediaMix Video Player?

Answer

Even though MediaMix Video Player supports all .SRT files, there are still some of them which are or must have been encoded differently. In such cases, it is strongly recommended to use a different subtitle file or one from another source.
